quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,30,"Ndipo pamene Ambuye wako adati kwa angelo: “Ine ndiika olamula padziko lapansi.” Iwo adati: “Kodi inu mudzaika padziko amene adzakhala ali kuchita zoipa ndi kukhetsa mwazi pamene ife tili kuyamika ndi kutamanda ulemerero wanu?” Iye adati: “Ine ndimadziwa zimene inu simudziwa.”"
  2,31,"Ndipo Iye adamuphunzitsa Adamu mayina a zinthu zonse ndipo adazisonkhanitsa pamaso pa angelo nati: “Ndiuzeni mayina a zinthu izi ngati ndinu achilungamo.”"
  2,32,"Iwo adati: “Ulemerero ukhale kwa Inu. Ife tilibe nzeru kupatula zokhazo zimene mutiphunzitsa. Ndithudi Inu nokha ndinu amene muli Wodziwa ndi Wanzeru.”"
  2,33,"Ndipo Mulungu adati: “Iwe Adamu! Auze mayina ake.” Ndipo pamene iye adatchula mayina a zinthuzo, Mulungu adati: “Kodi Ine sindidakuuzeni inu kuti Ine ndimadziwa zobisika za kumwamba ndi za dziko lapansi ndipo ndimadziwanso zonse zimene inu mumaulula ndi zimene mumabisa?”"
  2,34,"Ndipo pamene Ife tidati kwa angelo: “Mugwadireni Adamu.” Ndipo onse adamugwadira kupatula Satana amene adakana ndi kudzikweza ndipo adakala m’modzi wa osakhulupilira"
  2,35,"Ndipo Ife tidati: “oh Adamu! Khala iwe pamodzi ndi mkazi wako m’mundamo ndipo muzidya mmene mungafunire koma musadzayandikire mtengo uwu chifukwa mudzakhala anthu ochimwa.”"
  2,36,"Koma Satana adawanyenga ndipo adawachotsetsa m’munda m’mene iwo adali. Ife tidati: “Tsikani pansi nonse ndipo inu mudzakhala mdani wa wina ndi mnzake. Ndipo dziko lapansi ndi kumene inu mudzakhala ndi chisangalalo cha kanthawi kochepa.”"
  2,37,Ndipo Adamu adalandira mawu kuchokera kwa Ambuye wake. Ndipo Ambuye wake adamukhululukira iye. Ndithudi Iye ndi wokhululukira ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha